rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Word is that a massive fish has been
spotted off Baldotas Isle in the
Liberalitan Archipelago.

rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I heard that this fish has the most
delicious taste out of all God's
creations.

rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0004
rows.name: No wonder it's causing so much fuss!

rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Have to say, I can't stop thinking about
it myself!

rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0006
rows.name: What I'd give for a taste...

rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0007
rows.name:
But there's no way I could fish
that beast out by myself.

rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0008
rows.name:
So, I'm on the lookout for someone to
lend a hand, but no one seems to be
up for it.

rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0009
rows.name:
Can't pass over a chance like this
though, can we? Who knows when we'd
get another shot at it!

rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0010
rows.name:
Wow! You're going to help!
You're just the ticket!

rows.label: tlk46320171_04_msg0011
rows.name:
Come on, we'll be gorging on roasted
fish before long!
